Q-2-Common Element Between two List, print the number appear in both.
Ans
List<Integer> nums1 = new List<Integer>{3, 8, 12, 5, 9};
List<Integer> nums2 = new List<Integer>{8, 1, 5, 20}; 
Set<Integer> nums3= new Set<Integer>(nums2);
Set<Integer> finalNums= new Set<Integer>();
for(Integer nums: nums1){
    if(nums3.contains(nums)){
        finalNums.add(nums);
    }
}
System.debug(finalNums);
